{"id":53251,"date":"2024-01-22T18:38:31","date_gmt":"2024-01-22T13:08:31","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=53251"},"modified":"2024-02-20T20:59:02","modified_gmt":"2024-02-20T15:29:02","slug":"kitchen-trends-2024","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-trends-2024\/","title":{"rendered":"The Future of Cooking Spaces: Top Kitchen Design Trends in 2024"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>Kitchen Trends 2024 is for a personalised culinary experience!<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Bid goodbye to bold colour schemes, cluttered storage, cramped countertops, and those fatigued faces in the kitchen. Welcome the fresh kitchen trends of 2024. Just as a cosy bed with soft linens beckons us to a restful slumber, a well-designed, organised, and spacious kitchen sets the stage for a positive mindset and encourages culinary adventures. There&#8217;s undeniable truth in the influence of ambience on our state of mind. The trending ideas emerge as problem solvers, bringing style and luxury to transform your space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We turn to Designer Shikha Agarwal, the studio head at DesignCafe, Hyderabad, for insights into how these trends are reshaping the heart of our homes. Join us as we explore the flavours, textures, and designs that promise to elevate your kitchen experience.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">1. Innovative Kitchen Design Trends: Pantry Units!&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>No more cluttered corners! One kitchen design essential we often hear about is &#8211; <em>a pantry unit.<\/em> It&#8217;s a smart storage solution (like a store room!) for all your kitchen items and accessories. Whether it&#8217;s a pull-out unit, a walk-in space, or a pantry with a swing larder, a variety of sleek designs and space-saving mechanisms are available, all personalised for your kitchen needs. Check out this image showcasing a swing larder pantry unit, bringing items within easy reach from those hard-to-access spots.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit.jpg\" alt=\"Pantry unit leads the kitchen design trends in 2024 for clutter-free corners\" class=\"wp-image-53255\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183219\/kitchen-design-trends-pantry-unit-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Pantry units lead the charge in kitchen trends<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get your dream modular kitchen designed to make cooking easy\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/10\/23174442\/get-your-dream-modular-kitchen-designed-to-make-cooking-easy.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/kitchen-pantry-unit-design\/\">Kitchen Pantry Units here<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">2. In Kitchen Appliance Trends: Appliance Garage&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Bid farewell to crowded countertops with microwaves and mixers! The appliance garage trend revolutionises kitchens by offering dedicated spaces to store both small and large machines, ensuring a clean and organised countertop. An appliance garage or a tall unit can also be customised to fit multiple gadgets and match your interiors. Here&#8217;s a glimpse of a gorgeous neutral-themed space adorned with marble, showcasing an appliance garage featuring a built-in space for microwaves or ovens alongside cabinets and drawers for other smaller machines.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen appliance trends, appliance garages offer dedicated storage spaces, \nensuring a clean and organised countertop\n\" class=\"wp-image-53254\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183209\/kitchen-appliance-trends-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Build a tall unit in your new kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/choosing-appliances-for-your-kitchen\/\">Choosing Appliances for Your Kitchen<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">3. 2024 Kitchen Trends: Get Ready to Love &#8216;Islands&#8217;&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>This year&#8217;s home trends are all about convenience, modernity and innovation. In 2024 kitchen trends, islands are becoming more versatile and functional. Evolving from simple countertops, they now offer built-in storage, seating, and integrated sink units, making them the focal point of modern culinary heavens. Whether you are searching for extra space or a multifunctional breakfast nook, islands have become indispensable. Take a look at this picture showcasing an island with concealed storage and two high chairs, perfect for family gatherings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends.jpg\" alt=\"According to the 2024 kitchen trends, islands are becoming more versatile and functional\" class=\"wp-image-53252\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183146\/2024-kitchen-trends-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A kitchen island is a multifunctional helping hand<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">4. Latest Trends in Kitchen Cupboards for Water Purifiers<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The latest kitchen trends in 2024 introduce an innovative solution: an under-sink unit dedicated to water purifiers. Say goodbye to the cluttered wall space and tangled wires! Conceal your water purifier in an under-sink cabinet, connecting one tap for filtered drinking water and the other for regular use. It is modern, convenient, and ensures safety. Take a peek at this kitchen space, which showcases an under-sink cabinet for a water purifier, keeping the kitchen tidy and stylish.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards.jpg\" alt=\"Under-sink unit latest trends in kitchen cupboards for purifiers and ensures clutter-free walls\" class=\"wp-image-53259\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183256\/latest-trends-in-kitchen-cupboards-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A minimalist U-shaped kitchen<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Read more about <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/under-sink-storage-ideas\/\">Under sink Storage Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">5. Kitchen Style Trends Lean Towards Quartz Platforms<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Before getting your kitchen designed or renovated, one question generally lingers in homeowners&#8217; minds &#8211; which countertop is the most durable? This year, quartz is stealing the spotlight! Quartz platforms are preferred for their durability, low maintenance (no sealing required), and extensive variety in colours and patterns, offering a hygienic, consistent, and visually appealing option for kitchen surfaces. Look at this lavish <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/quartz-countertops\/\">quartz countertop<\/a> with an integrated hob unit that beautifully complements the neutral cabinet tones.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen style trends lean towards quartz platforms due to their hygienic properties, consistent quality, and visual appeal\" class=\"wp-image-53256\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183228\/kitchen-style-trends-with-quartz-platform-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Quartz is the ultimate countertop choice<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">6. Trendy Modern Kitchen Wall Colours: Pick Neutral Tones<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Out with bold colours, in with subtle, neutral tones! In 2024, the focus is on creating serene and inviting kitchen spaces adorned with gentle hues that radiate relaxation. Amidst the stresses of everyday living, choosing soothing colours can make a world of difference. Opt for beige, white, cream, or grey shades for your walls. These hues bring simplicity and openness to your space. Take a look at this kitchen adorned in a neutral colour palette of white and light pastels, featuring handleless cabinets, crystal drop pendant lights, and a stunning island table with additional storage and seating.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours.jpg\" alt=\"Neutral tones are the trendy modern kitchen wall colours for inviting space\" class=\"wp-image-53260\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183305\/trendy-modern-kitchen-wall-colours-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Neutral tones are trending this season<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">7. Kitchen Tiles&#8217; Latest Trends: Pop-Up Colours for the WOW Factor!<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>While the walls maintain a minimalistic vibe, the tiles can add that splash of colour you seek! The kitchen interior trends of 2024 emphasise the importance of vibrant tiles, particularly in the backsplash, infusing energy and personality into your space. Tiles often come in various designs, such as the Moroccan style, and can serve as the focal point or accent wall for a single-toned space. Take a peek at this room boasting a copper palette with refreshing yellow tiles in the backsplash, paired with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/white-kitchen-countertops\/\">pristine white countertop<\/a> and a hint of gold in the kitchen faucet.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends.jpg\" alt=\"Latest kitchen tile trends emphasise the importance of vibrant colour\" class=\"wp-image-53258\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183248\/latest-kitchen-tile-trends-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Say YES to vibrant colours<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">8. Handle Evolution: Kitchen Design Trends 2023, 2024\u2026&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Handles are undergoing a makeover! Designs like edge-profile and Gola designs are gaining popularity by offering a seamless and modern look. Remember, style is in the details. While there is nothing wrong with regular ones, modern handles will definitely elevate your kitchen. Investing in these transformative details for your dream home interiors is a choice worth making. This kitchen flaunts cabinets with profile handles featuring exposed edges for improved grip and style.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen trends in 2023 and 2024 show increased popularity in handle designs with edge-profile and Gola designs\" class=\"wp-image-53253\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183159\/handle-evoluion-kitchen-trends-2023-2024-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Witness a handle evolution<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">9. Lastly, Embracing &#8216;Two Sinks&#8217; In 2024 Kitchen Trends<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Two sinks? Yes, it&#8217;s a trend! Increased storage options and larger sinks in utility areas make kitchens more organised and functional. While having two full kitchens might not be practical for many, having <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/modular-kitchen-interiors\/double-bowl-kitchen-sink\/\">two separate sinks<\/a> is a viable option. One sink in the utility area caters to messy cleaning and dirty utensils, while the other in the kitchen serves for basic washing and cooking needs. This separation promotes a cleaner kitchen ambience, offers more space, and provides a modern approach to culinary experiences.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024.jpg\" alt=\"Kitchen trends in 2024 welcome two sinks, separating mess from prep for a cleaner, more organised space\" class=\"wp-image-53261\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024-50x30.jpg 50w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/01\/22183314\/two-sinks-kitchen-trends-in-2024-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">2024 kitchen trends welcome two sinks in one house!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>This year, kitchens are evolving into sophisticated, functional, and stylish spaces, marrying innovation with design. As we enter 2024, keep an eye on these kitchen design trends as they hold transformative powers to elevate your culinary haven, seamlessly integrating technology, aesthetics, and functionality. Exciting times ahead for interior design aficionados!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to get your space designed, have a chat with our expert designers today!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Modular Kitchens At Best Prices<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Speak to our kitchen experts today!<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\